item.title: CVE-2017-6143|2024-09-16T16:18:23.499Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- big-ip%20%28afm%2C%20asm%29
item.description: X509 certificate verification was not correctly implemented in the IP Intelligence Subscription and IP Intelligence feed-list features, and thus the remote server's identity is not properly validated in F5 BIG-IP 12.0.0-12.1.2, 11.6.0-11.6.2, or 11.5.0-11.5.5.
